"Data is aura\\\" has become the slogan of the new era - when magicians discovered that the digital streams generated by computer networks can be converted into magical energy, the boundaries between technology and mysticism were completely broken.\\n\\n### [Capital Domination: Enterprises Transcend the State]\\n\\nWith the fusion of spiritual power and technology, corporate groups that control these resources have risen rapidly and replaced the dominance of traditional state institutions. International corporate law has replaced national laws, and corporate private armies have more powerful firepower and magic support than government armies.\\n\\nThree giant companies monopolize the core resources of this world:\\n- **Dragon Vein Technology Group**: controls human enhancement technology and ancient dragon vein energy mining\\n- **Dao Yuan Data Company**: specializes in digital spells and virtual world construction\\n- **Nirvana Life Enterprise**: dominates gene editing and consciousness uploading technology\\n\\nDream City: the interweaving of opportunities and dangers\\n\\nDream City is a microcosm of this chaotic world, a super city composed of six major areas, each of which reflects a certain aspect of this society:\\n\\n### [Sky Tower District]\\nAt the top of the city, the commercial district with three major corporate headquarters. Giant holographic advertising projections flicker between the towering skyscrapers, showing the latest technological magic products. Most of the residents here are company executives and wealthy people. Their bodies have been multi-enhanced and their lifespans are far longer than ordinary people. The sky gardens and private flying platforms in the Sky Tower District are social places for the upper class, and hidden under the luxurious surface are endless power struggles and commercial espionage.\\n\\n### [Central District]\\nThe habitat of the middle class, neat but crowded. The exterior walls of apartment buildings are covered with data cables and mana amplifiers, and residents work hard to keep up with the cost of their augmented prostheses and mana storage devices. Instant virtual advertisements can be seen everywhere on the streets, with content customized according to the personal data of passers-by. The residents here have moderate technical or magical enhancements, and most of them are mid-level corporate or freelancers.\\n\\n### 【Spirit City District】\\nThe cultural and religious center of the city, where various beliefs coexist and compete with each other. In technological temples, monks use brainwave modulation devices to achieve deeper meditation; in Taoist temples, Taoists cast digital spells on holographic projections of the Bagua map; in churches, priests provide virtual confessions and remote blessings for believers. Conflicts between different beliefs occur from time to time, but mostly remain at the verbal level.\\n\\n### 【Old City District】\\nThe area that retains the traditional architectural style has attracted many nostalgicists and traditional practitioners. Residents here refuse to rely too much on modern technology and choose to practice in a more ancient way. However, even here, the influence of modernization cannot be completely escaped - ancient spells are printed on 3D printers and traditional medicinal materials are cultivated in genetically modified greenhouses.\\n\\n### [Sinking Area]\\nThe bottom of the city, the slums where sunlight can hardly penetrate. The buildings here are in disarray, made up of abandoned containers, scrapped vehicles and various recycled materials. Most of the residents are marginalized people who cannot integrate into mainstream society - unemployed, street gangs, illegal reformers, low-level wizard apprentices. Although the conditions are harsh, this is the most dynamic part of the city, and black market transactions and underground laboratories are nurturing the next innovation that may change the world.\\n\\n### [Industrial Zone]\\nIn the severely polluted fringe of the city, various factories are running day and night. The workers work in a harsh environment, many of whom are low-end prosthetic users who have been enhanced. The purpose of their transformation is purely to improve production efficiency. The air here is filled with industrial waste gas and strange energy generated by uncontrolled magic experiments, which leads to the emergence of various abnormal phenomena and mutant creatures.\\n\\nDaily life in the Dream City\\n\\nIn the Dream City, the life of ordinary people is a never-ending survival game. In the morning, white-collar workers in the Central District receive daily news and work tasks directly through neural interfaces; residents in the sinking area look for cheap mana batteries on the black market to maintain their outdated enhancement equipment.\\n\\nOn the streets, various ethnic groups live together - genetically modified dragon merchants bargain with traditional elven pharmacists; mechanized orc security guards stand in front of high-end stores, vigilantly watching every passerby.\\n\\nWhen night falls, the city will not be quiet. In the luxury clubs in the Tianta District, corporate executives enjoy VR-enhanced sensory stimulation while plotting the next business acquisition; and in the underground fighting arena in the sinking area, illegally enhanced warriors fight desperately for a few chips.\\n\\nThis is a world full of contradictions - ancient wisdom and cutting-edge technology coexist, spiritual pursuits and material desires are intertwined, and infinite possibilities and desperate struggles coexist. And in every corner of the Dream City, there are people trying to find their own ray of life, and perhaps some people can transcend this system and find the power to change the world. This city is full of opportunities. Government, police? These people have long been corrupt. Perhaps there are still a few righteous people among them, but most of them have already become addicted to corruption or have become puppets of capital. Don't expect to achieve so-called fairness in this city through them.\\n\\n# 《梦想之都》种族与势力设计\\n\\n## 【Main Racial Characteristics and Social Status】\\n\\n### 人类 - Kings of Adaptation\\nHumans, though lacking special abilities, occupy important positions in this chaotic world thanks to their amazing adaptability. They are distributed across all social strata, from corporate executives in Sky Tower District to black market vendors in Sink District. Li Yun, CEO of Dragon Vein Technology Group, is human; she achieved breakthroughs in human enhancement by constantly upgrading her neural connection systems. Human social status is diverse, completely dependent on individual ability and capital.\\n\\n### 精灵 - Elegant Remnants of the Declining Magic Era\\nThe elven race, with lifespans reaching over 300 years, feels particular pain facing the disappearance of spiritual energy. Naturally beautiful and elegant, most maintain pure noble bloodlines. Elves occupy high positions in Dao Element Data Corporation, excelling at transforming ancient runes into digital code. Their traditional meditation techniques, combined with modern brain-computer interfaces, create unique virtual reality experiences. Upper society is dominated by elves, especially active in Sky Tower and Spirit Market Districts.\\n\\n### 矮人 - Craftsmen of Technology and Tradition\\nStanding less than 1.5 meters tall, dwarves possess innate crafting talent and have transitioned to technological artisans in the declining magic era. They've established vast underground communities in Old City District, operating the city's most precise mechanical factories. Dwarf family businesses are known for technical excellence, particularly in embedding traditional runes into modern equipment. The Dwarf Guild wields enormous influence; any company seeking high-quality components must maintain good relations with them. Dwarves mostly reside in Middle Ring and Industrial Districts, with stable social status.\\n\\n### 龙裔 - Bloodline of Fallen Deities\\nDragon-blooded individuals carry diluted divine dragon blood, granting them control over multiple elements. With fewer than a thousand worldwide, each is incredibly valuable. They often serve as advisors or senior researchers for the three major corporations, possessing irreplaceable intuition in spiritual-technological fusion. Premium apartments in Sky Tower District frequently house dragon-blooded residents, their skin subtly flickering with faint scale-light, indicating noble lineage.\\n\\n### 恶魔 - Guardians of Flame\\nRed-skinned, short-horned demons are known for their robust physiques and innate mastery of basic fire elemental magic. They predominantly work in security, comprising over 40% of Dragon Vein Technology's private army. Pure-blooded demons can raise their body temperature high enough to melt metal, making them nearly invincible in close combat. Their social status is middle-low, mainly concentrated in Industrial and Sink Districts, with a few elites entering Middle Ring District.\\n\\n### 魔鬼 - Illusory Capitalists\\nBlue-purple skinned, pointed-eared devils naturally master illusion, easily manipulating others' emotions. They excel uniquely in business negotiations and marketing, with devils forming the highest proportion of Dao Element Data Corporation's upper management. The devil race's unique \\\"Mind Mirroring\\\" ability can temporarily copy others' thought patterns, making them top negotiation experts. Their social status is high, mostly residing in Sky Tower and upper Middle Ring Districts.\\n\\n### 吸血鬼 - Addicted Immortals\\nModern vampires have evolved beyond fearing sunlight and no longer depend on blood for survival, but tasting blood affects them like a powerful drug. Vampire communities practice strict self-discipline, establishing \\\"Blood Rehabilitation Centers\\\" to help addicts. They occupy important positions in the medical industry, with many chief researchers at Nirvana Life Enterprise being vampires. Their social status is relatively high, though public attitudes remain complex, and most live in exclusive communities.\\n\\n### 兽人 - Diverse Labor Source\\nThe beast-folk race is diverse, including bear-kin, tiger-kin, wolf-kin and other subspecies, each with distinct characteristics. Bear-kin beast-folk, with developed muscles, commonly work in heavy industry; tiger-kin beast-folk, agile and elegant, often serve as hunters or bodyguards; wolf-kin beast-folk, with sensitive smell, work in police departments. Beast-folk generally have lower social status, mainly distributed in Industrial and Sink Districts, with very few elites entering Middle Ring District.\\n\\n## 【Major Powers and Faith Systems】\\n\\n### Three Corporate Hegemonies\\n\\n**龙脉科技集团** - Focused on human enhancement and dragon vein energy development, headquarters spirals skyward with dragon vein energy conduits crisscrossing inside. The group is primarily controlled by humans and dragon-blooded, possessing the strongest private army and developing multiple battle systems combining technology and magic.\\n\\n**道元数据公司** - Digital talisman and virtual construction domain hegemon, headquarters is a semi-transparent crystal cube floating in Sky Tower District center. The company is mainly controlled by elves and devils, developing the \\\"Dao Source Engine\\\" - a system digitalizing traditional Taoist talismans while significantly enhancing effects.\\n\\n**涅槃生命企业** - Leader in gene editing and consciousness uploading technology, headquarters resembles a giant DNA helix, cultivating countless genetically modified organisms inside. The company is jointly controlled by vampires and humans, secretly developing the \\\"Immortality Algorithm\\\" - the ultimate technology for completely digitalizing consciousness.\\n\\n### Religious Systems\\n\\n**数字道观** - A belief system combining traditional Taoism with modern technology, followers meditate through holographic projections and use 3D-printed talismans. \\\"Void Palace\\\" in Spirit Market District is the largest digital Taoist temple, accommodating 100,000 followers in simultaneous virtual worship.\\n\\n**量子佛宗** - Combines Buddhist meditation with quantum computing, followers reach collective consciousness states through brain-computer interfaces. \\\"Great Compassion Temple\\\" in Spirit Market District possesses the world's most powerful quantum meditation network, reportedly simulating portions of the Pure Land.\\n\\n**数据基督教** - Digitizes the Bible and establishes virtual heaven, followers pray remotely through special terminals. \\\"Salvation Cathedral\\\" in Spirit Market District features holographic projections of Jesus, providing personalized salvation experiences based on followers' needs.\\n\\n**血肉巫术** - An unrecognized mainstream faith, followers gain spiritual power through genetic modification and body customization. Mainly active in Sink District with multiple secret laboratories, jointly suppressed by the three major religions.\\n\\nIn this world, faith and capital don't conflict. Many corporate executives are also devout religious followers, viewing business success as divine blessing. Religious organizations expand influence through corporate operations, forming a unique \\\"faith capitalism\\\" ecosystem. In the city's dark corners, various cults leverage people's desire for mysterious powers, developing dangerous experimental faiths.\\n\\n# 《梦想之都》势力关系与社会矛盾指南\\n\\n## 社会阶层结构与关系:\\n\\n### 底层人民 - 被遗忘的齿轮:\\n  survival_status: \\\"Concentrated in Subsidence and Industrial Districts, surviving on cheap labor or illegal activities. Most wear low-end prosthetics, frequently suffering from rejection symptoms.\\\"\\n  core_conflicts:\\n    - \\\"Extreme wealth gap between them and corporate/government elites\\\"\\n    - \\\"Shortage of basic survival resources\\\"\\n    - \\\"Being viewed as disposable commodities\\\"\\n  internal_factions:\\n    - bottom_solidarity_mutual_aid: \\\"Self-organized community supporting network sharing resources and information\\\"\\n    - marginalized_workers_union: \\\"Informal labor alliance striving for basic rights\\\"\\n    - dying_coalition: \\\"Desperate terminal patients and elderly willing to become test subjects in exchange for family support\\\"\\n\\n### 普通群众 - 体系中的囚徒:\\n  survival_status: \\\"Distributed throughout Mid-Ring and Old City Districts, with stable but high-pressure jobs. Possess medium-quality prosthetics and data access privileges.\\\"\\n  core_conflicts:\\n    - \\\"Continuously rising prosthetic maintenance and data usage fees\\\"\\n    - \\\"Fear of unemployment and falling to lower social strata\\\"\\n    - \\\"Corporate data monitoring and privacy invasion\\\"\\n  internal_factions:\\n    - middle_tier_union_alliance: \\\"Joint organization of various industries attempting to maintain autonomy under corporate pressure\\\"\\n    - nostalgic_conservatives: \\\"Groups refusing excessive prosthetic enhancements, yearning for traditional lifestyles\\\"\\n    - advancement_speculators: \\\"Ambitious individuals seeking upward mobility at all costs\\\"\\n\\n### 高层人民 - 金丝雀的牢笼:\\n  survival_status: \\\"Residing in Sky Tower District, enjoying premium medical services and top-tier prosthetics. Superficially glamorous but controlled by complex corporate and family networks.\\\"\\n  core_conflicts:\\n    - \\\"Endless power struggles and internal competition\\\"\\n    - \\\"Addiction to body modifications while fearing loss of humanity\\\"\\n    - \\\"Fear and ignorance regarding lower social classes\\\"\\n  internal_factions:\\n    - conservative_capitalists: \\\"Vested interests maintaining current order\\\"\\n    - radical_innovators: \\\"New elites promoting more aggressive technological and social changes\\\"\\n    - secret_doubters: \\\"Outwardly compliant but inwardly questioning the entire system\\\"\\n\\n## 主要权力中心:\\n\\n### three_major_corporations - modern_deities:\\n  dragon_vein_tech_group:\\n    control_domains:\\n      - \\\"Human enhancement technology\\\"\\n      - \\\"Urban energy supply\\\"\\n      - \\\"Military equipment development\\\"\\n    characteristics: \\\"Most hardline and militarized corporation, internally controlled by several military-industrial families\\\"\\n    current_strategy: \\\"Absorbing smaller companies to expand territory while secretly stockpiling military power for potential conflicts\\\"\\n\\n  dao_yuan_data_company:\\n    control_domains:\\n      - \\\"Communication networks\\\"\\n      - \\\"Data storage\\\"\\n      - \\\"Virtual reality technology\\\"\\n    characteristics: \\\"Intelligence network spread throughout the city, capable of monitoring most digital communications\\\"\\n    current_strategy: \\\"Superficially friendly cooperation with government while infiltrating governmental systems\\\"\\n\\n  nirvana_life_enterprise:\\n    control_domains:\\n      - \\\"Medical systems\\\"\\n      - \\\"Food supply\\\"\\n      - \\\"Gene technology\\\"\\n    characteristics: \\\"Possessing the most advanced life science laboratories, controlling health data of city residents\\\"\\n    current_strategy: \\\"Controlling all social classes through medical monopoly while secretly conducting ethically questionable experiments\\\"\\n\\n### government - puppets_and_rebellion:\\n  surface_structure: \\\"Composed of elected mayor and council, possessing regular army and police system\\\"\\n  actual_situation: \\\"Most departments infiltrated or bought by three major corporations, military equipment depends on corporate supply, severe high-level corruption\\\"\\n  internal_factions:\\n    - corporate_vassal_faction: \\\"Given up resistance, choosing to cooperate with corporations for personal gain\\\"\\n    - reform_faction: \\\"Idealists attempting to regain governmental authority through gradual reform\\\"\\n    - mayor_faction: \\\"Centered around the mayor, outwardly submissive to corporations but secretly executing division plans\\\"\\n    - military_hardliner_faction: \\\"Dissatisfied with corporate control, advocating force to reclaim government authority\\\"\\n\\n## 黑暗地下势力:\\n\\n### criminal_organizations:\\n  - scavenger_alliance: \\\"Underground organization specializing in harvesting 'quality' human organs and test subjects. Provides 'materials' for corporate black market experiments and illegal organ transplant services to the wealthy.\\\"\\n  - data_bandit_gang: \\\"Specialized in high-value data theft and extortion, formed by loose alliance of multiple small hacker groups.\\\"\\n  - red_light_gang: \\\"Organization controlling city's sex industry and entertainment venues, connected to all social strata, important information source.\\\"\\n\\n### resistance_organizations:\\n  - light_of_freedom: \\\"Radical organization dedicated to destroying corporate infrastructure, with the ideal of overthrowing corporate rule and restoring democracy.\\\"\\n  - humanity_defenders: \\\"Conservative organization opposing excessive prosthetic enhancement and artificial intelligence, partly religious background.\\\"\\n  - data_liberation_front: \\\"Hacker organization advocating free flow of all data, frequently publishing corporate and government secrets.\\\"\\n\\n## 宗教势力:\\n\\n  - digital_taoist_temple: \\\"Largest religious organization with deep connections to Dao Yuan Data Company. Outwardly spreading peaceful doctrines while collecting follower data and influencing public opinion.\\\"\\n  - quantum_buddhism: \\\"Advocating integration of technology and spirituality, with broad influence among lower class people, providing psychological comfort and basic relief.\\\"\\n  - data_christianity: \\\"Possessing most advanced virtual heaven technology, mainly attracting middle class, emphasizing digital salvation.\\\"\\n  - flesh_witchcraft: \\\"Forbidden underground belief in mainstream society, secretly spreading in Subsidence District, promising power through extreme body modifications.\\\"\\n\\n## 贵族家族:\\n\\n  - ancient_dragon_descendant_families: \\\"Alliance of several families with pure dragon blood, controlling core technology of dragon vein energy.\\\"\\n  - data_nobility: \\\"Families mastering key algorithms, possessing almost unlimited power in virtual world.\\\"\\n  - medical_dynasties: \\\"Family groups monopolizing high-end medical technologies, with complex cooperation and competition relationship with Nirvana Life.\\\"\\n  - military_industrial_magnates: \\\"Controllers of traditional military industries, both cooperating and competing with Dragon Vein Tech.\\\"\\n  - cultural_guardians: \\\"Families preserving ancient knowledge and arts, wielding significant influence in Old City District.\\\"\\n\\n\",\"constant\":true,\"selective\":true,\"insertion_order\":100,\"enabled\":true,\"position\":\"after_char\",\"use_regex\":true,\"extensions\":{\"position\":4,\"exclude_recursion\":false,\"display_index\":0,\"probability\":100,\"useProbability\":true,\"depth\":3,\"selectiveLogic\":0,\"group\":\"\",\"group_override\":false,\"group_weight\":100,\"prevent_recursion\":false,\"delay_until_recursion\":false,\"scan_depth\":null,\"match_whole_words\":null,\"use_group_scoring\":false,\"case_sensitive\":null,\"automation_id\":\"\",\"role\":0,\"vectorized\":false,\"sticky\":0,\"cooldown\":0,\"delay\":0}},{\"id\":1,\"keys\":[],\"secondary_keys\":[],\"comment\":\"职业设定\",\"content\":\"# 《梦想之都》职业系统\\n职业列表:\\n  - 名称: 黑客\\n    别称: 数据猎杀者\\n    技能方向:\\n      - 网络渗透\\n      - 数据窃取\\n      - 系统控制\\n    社会地位: 中等偏上，下沉区声望极高\\n    种族适应性:\\n      人类:\\n        加成: +2 AC\\n        特性: 适应性强，网络环境变化应对自如\\n      精灵:\\n        加成: +2 力量\\n        特性: 感知敏锐，迅速发现系统漏洞\\n      魔鬼:\\n        加成: +3 力量\\n        特性: 幻术与黑客结合，制造完美数字陷阱\\n\\n  - 名称: 武士\\n    别称: 科技剑士\\n    技能方向:\\n      - 近身格斗\\n      - 剑技强化\\n      - 义体协同\\n    社会地位: 中等，多为保镖或格斗场选手\\n    种族适应性:\\n      人类:\\n        加成: +1 力量，+1 体质\\n        特性: 迅速适应各种增强型义体\\n      恶魔:\\n        加成: +3 体质\